<i>noun</i>: 허무감 [허무감], 허무 [허무], 허망 [허망] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>허무감 [허무감]</dt><br>
<dd>futility; emptiness</dd><br>
<dd>가치 없고 의미 없게 느껴져 매우 허전하고 쓸쓸한 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of finding something worthless and meaningless, feeling extremely empty and lonely.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>허무 [허무]</dt><br>
<dd>futility; emptiness</dd><br>
<dd>가치 없고 의미 없게 느껴져 매우 허전하고 쓸쓸함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of thinking of something as worthless and meaningless, making one feel extremely empty and lonely.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>허망 [허망]</dt><br>
<dd>1. falsehood; untruth</dd><br>
<dd>거짓되고 믿음이 가지 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>A quality of being false and unreliable.</dd><br>
<dd>2. futility; being in vain</dd><br>
<dd>어이없고 아무 보람이 없음.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being absurd and fruitless.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>